metadata.name: OneCool Collective: Run Cool
metadata.description: OneCool Collective: Run Cool is the first apparel collection of the “OneCool Collective” NFT series, hosted on the Ethereum blockchain, brought together by One Cool Group: Asia’s leading entertainment group and Gusto Collective: Asia’s first Brand-Tech group, with a collective workforce of over 400 staff around the world. Named by our OCCIA community, Run Cool is created to celebrate Warriors of Future’s launch on Netflix and our first Metaverse Exhibition co-created with Wear Digital.
